    <p>Facebook: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/natamon.wittayapoom" class="underline text-orange-200" target="_blank">natamon wittayapoom</a></p>
    <p>Instagram: <a href="https://www.instagram.com/natamon_wittayapoom" class="underline text-orange-200" target="_blank">@natamon_wittayapoom</a></p>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
